    "name": "Hyperbolic Image Generation API",
    "description": "Generate images from text prompts using diffusion models hosted by Hyperbolic \u2014 Stable Diffusion XL, Stable Diffusion 3.5, FLUX.1 [schnell] and FLUX.1 [dev] (sunset), and ControlNet variants. Custom LoRA support. Pricing starts at $0.0025 per image.\n\n\nContact Support:\n Name: Hyperbolic Support\n Email: support@hyperbolic.ai",
